-- Monte Paschi shares suspended limit down  
-- By Silvia Aloisi and Andrea Mandala
-- Thu Nov 06, 2014 03:45AM EST
-- None



MILAN, Nov 6 (Reuters) - Shares in Italy's Monte dei Paschi di Siena <BMPS.MI> were suspended for excessive losses on Thursday after the bank approved a rights issue of up to 2.5 billion euros ($3.1 billion) to plug a capital shortfall laid bare by European checks.

